    "id": "alanesLily2",
    "title": "alanesLily2",
    "date": "2023-12-31",
    "medium": "watercolor",
    "dimensions": "",
    "tags": [],
    "description": "Alane gave us a lily when they were visiting. Every year it comes up with bright happy pink blooms with yellow stamens. I tried to capture the fragility of the petals as well as the lush green of the leaves.",
